				<h3>FAQ:</h3>

				<div class="faq-entry">
					<strong>Why should I come here?</strong><br />	
					While Halo Waypoint is an incridebly well built website, it's a bit overkill for just looking at stats. Branch offers a much simplier approach that takes away all the clutter and tries to just show you exactly what you want to know about that 1v1 against that kid in matchmaking.
				</div>

				<div class="faq-entry">
					<strong>How often can I update my stats?</strong><br />
					It depends on the stats. Service Records, Commendations, Game Histories, and Specilizations update every 8 minutes. A Match's History never update, as they <strong><sup>should</sup></strong> never change.
				</div>

